21 A. Each person who makes an application for issuance of a policy of
22 insurance covering a motorcycle shall provide proof of the appropriate license
23 endorsement required by R.S. 32:408(C). Such The proof shall be provided to the
24 insurer or its producer within ninety days of application for such policy. If the policy
25 of insurance is issued by an insurer that does not maintain an office in this state, then
26 the person may submit a sworn affidavit that he has the proper license endorsement
